cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper discusses online learning algorithms for regret minimization, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the issue of tuning parameters and learning in unbounded domains, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of convex analysis and surrogate losses suggests that the paper may also be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
